= News

Created by Pascal Naef (ScreenConcept), November 2008

With this news extension you can enter news with headline, leadtext and text. A news will be only displayed if start is greater or equal current date and stop is less or equal current date.

Requirements
For this extension rails plugin calendar data select plugin is required. Further informations are you find here: http://code.google.com/p/calendardateselect/ .


Installation


Usage
<r:news_current>
  <r:news_headline /><br />
  <r:news_leadtext /><br />
  <r:news_text />
</r:news_current>

<r:news_marquee [behavior="scroll"] [direction="left"] [loop="true"] [scrollamount="1"] [scrolldelay="2"] />


